      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just stuck in this same shitty loop over and over. every time i think i finally fixed something or got my life together it just falls apart again. new job, lose it. try to stay sober, relapse. try to love someone, ruin it. it’s like i’m programmed to fail. i'm just so tired of starting over.",
