      "content": "it's not just about \"tools\" though. it's the fact that the loop is the only constant. some people are just meant to be stuck. i feel like i'm just spinning my wheels in the mud until i run out of gas. the only way to actually stop the noise and the reset is to just... not play the game anymore. the loop only ends one way.",
